</paragraph>
<paragraph id="0755A263FF71FF3BA7D1FD2AFAB1DF29" blockId="232.[189,1399,599,808]" pageId="232" pageNumber="233">
<keyLead id="BC1B0156FF71FF3BA7D1FD2AFAB1DF29" pageId="232" pageNumber="233">
– Pedipalp femur with four dorsal spines; pedipalp patella with five dorsal spines; cheliceral claw with six teeth; leg IV distitibia with nine 
<emphasis id="359E7E71FF71FF3BA581FD05FD6FDF02" box="[657,681,746,771]" italics="true" pageId="232" pageNumber="233">sc</emphasis>
and 
<emphasis id="359E7E71FF71FF3BA5F2FD06FD30DF02" box="[738,758,745,771]" italics="true" pageId="232" pageNumber="233">sf</emphasis>
